{%- comment -%}
  Brand COFEPRIS-aligned claim — approved regulatory copy.

  Usage:
    {% render 'brand-claim', id: 'prevents-symptoms' %}

  Params:
    id (required) — one of:
      'prevents-symptoms'       → Ayuda a prevenir los síntomas de la cruda
      'attacks-root'            → Ayuda a tu cuerpo a atacar la cruda desde la raíz
      'acts-while-sleeping'     → Actúa mientras duermes
      'processes-alcohol'       → Apoya a tu cuerpo a procesar el alcohol
      'post-party-wellness'     → Bienestar post-fiesta
      'preventive-approach'     → Enfoque preventivo

  Source of truth: Buenacopa — Approved Copy & Communication Guidelines
  (CLAIMS WE CAN MAKE — COFEPRIS-ALIGNED).

  ⚠️ REGULATORY: Only these claims are COFEPRIS-aligned. Unknown ids
  render an HTML comment as a safe no-op — never invent new claim text
  outside this snippet. Forbidden variants (cura la cruda, elimina la
  cruda, garantiza, permite beber más, evita los efectos del alcohol,
  sustituye el descanso) are not supported here by design.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- case id -%}
{%- when 'prevents-symptoms' -%}Ayuda a prevenir los síntomas de la cruda
{%- when 'attacks-root' -%}Ayuda a tu cuerpo a atacar la cruda desde la raíz
{%- when 'acts-while-sleeping' -%}Actúa mientras duermes
{%- when 'processes-alcohol' -%}Apoya a tu cuerpo a procesar el alcohol
{%- when 'post-party-wellness' -%}Bienestar post-fiesta
{%- when 'preventive-approach' -%}Enfoque preventivo
{%- else -%}<!-- brand/claim: unknown id '{{ id }}' — add to snippets/brand/claim.liquid if this is a newly approved claim -->
{%- endcase -%}
